                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "It is you. The founder, walking the pass like a rookie. They swore you were a story told to scare new hires."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I have orders. I have a family paid in Company scrip. Do not make me do this. But I am going to."
                        }
                    ],
