                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You are standing in an active yield zone. The family that mismanaged Frostfallow has been transitioned to alternative outcomes, and the parcel now performs. Rows under frost. Numbers. Ice and performance."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I run a string of fields off one clipboard. Frostfallow is the cold one - the Company likes a field that keeps, and a field that keeps does not spoil while the ledger catches up."
                        }
